{"tid":2479110,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［即時新聞］銅鑼灣廣場超大火","createTime":"2021-04-07T14:30:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T14:34:29.000Z","uid":391580,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8e52f92fd63a87d6a14776156aef7f203e987a60","tid":2479110,"uid":391580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T14:30:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3491268\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3491268&d=kuRIuFMgKSvsW5TefiiiYfUbXA8pdDK36CymbYVYMuw%3D&h=c5da2575\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3491268&h=0ab76365\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3491268</a><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國安徽省當地<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">銅鑼灣廣場</span></span></strong>今（6日）發生嚴重大火，1棟商業大樓被猛烈火勢吞噬，幾公里外都可看見濃密黑煙直衝天際，官方聲稱事故造成4死2傷，後續調查工作正在進行中。<br />\n<br />\n綜合中國官媒報導，安徽省應急管理廳指出，今天上午8點52分，池州市貴池區銅鑼灣廣場商業大樓發生火警，400平方公尺全面燃燒，現場畫面能見該大樓不斷噴出烈焰，伴隨著濃密黑煙直衝天際，景象相當嚇人，許多民眾都拿起手機記錄驚悚畫面，這場大火在1個小時過後才被撲滅。<br />\n<br />\n安徽省應急管理廳最新消息聲稱，在事故現場共計搜出6名受困火場的人員，立即送往醫院急救後已有2人出院，但當中有4人搶救無效死亡，中國警方與相關單位目前正在調查事故發生原因，同時進行其他善後處置工作。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmb6UkFPS6xMCSzsivF2anQbf5Z5EJoEXZYUBTkcdDzD1i?filename=wVPQkSN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwVPQkSN.jpg&h=a8f74ff2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0479773e34b7ca788962b0e2ce5c4fbfeb6ad130","tid":2479110,"uid":228868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T14:31:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f86100642b4c4a392446331e7f4fc817ba8e3a9d","tid":2479110,"uid":199670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T14:34:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"259216cdaa3e4604aee1b8af575d02715851eb32","tid":2479110,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T14:34:29.000Z","msg":"鍾共打手勿回<br />\n<br />\n樓豬簡介：<br />\n- 用小米機<br />\n- 用支那 APP<br />\n- 用 HK01 賣港 APP<br />\n- 鍾共培生會粉絲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連登培生培心會員討論區（1）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2476780\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2476780</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmemgqePMhWydUc2rxg7daoYiPvjaeRZpA8TfMhXCexT3Z?filename=RSsFtA2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRSsFtA2.png&h=c68c0e47&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}